</span></h3><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-15_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Communication and language are fundamental skills that children need to develop early in life. These skills are critical for personal, social, and academic growth. Unfortunately, some children face difficulties in these areas, which can significantly impact their development.
